{
  "stem": "8352.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was working in a gasoline factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was called Brabag.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We-- it was about four and a half to five miles march, one way.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we were about 250, 300 people, in a line of four, marching down the street to the factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When we came to the gate they counted how many this, this SS takes, how many he takes us out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The same amount he had to bring back in the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were counted going out of the gate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were counted coming back in the gate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were, I'll tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the beginning, we could march.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We don't have to walk too fast, just walk normal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On every few lines, we had the SS with the rifles, walking with us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you could not run away, you couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We walked into the factory there, and they told us what to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Dig ditches.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They gave us shovels.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we had to take that cable from that big wheel, and put on our shoulder and stretch it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Put it down so they connect it somehow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The German engineers were connecting those electric cables.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was our work we were assigned to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were doing this day after day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, if you were tall, in the back was you-- of you, in the back was a shorter person, you carried the whole weight of that cable on your shoulder.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The other one was making himself he carries, so you had twice as much pain on that shoulder.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They made us walking faster and running with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were kicking us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They said, you have to do it fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "When we were working on those ditches, they assigned one of our guys to be a kapo.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
